<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lanthorn" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lanthorn</orth> (O. Edd.) or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Lantern</orth> (some M. Edd.) 1) a transparent case for a candle: <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 3, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.136.61" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 136</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.1.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 1, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 55</bibl> (quibbling with <emph>horn</emph>). <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.3.25" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 3, 25</bibl> <emph>(my guide and l. to my feet).</emph><lb />2) a turret full of windows, by means of which cathedrals are illuminated: <cit><quote>a grave? O, no! a l., slaughtered youth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 84</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>